Hotel des Batignolles
description:
A cozy 2 star hotel in the west-end of Paris, located in the 17th arrondissement nearby Parc Marceau. It is close to two metro stations: "Rome" and "Place de Clichy", and on foot it is only 10 minutes from Moulin Rouge and 20 minutes from Montmartre and the Sacré Coeur. All 32 sound-proofed rooms include heat/AC, private bathroom (shower or bathtub), direct telephone, satellite TV and WiFi, priced at around 62€ - 77€ for a basic double. From 7:30 AM to 10 AM every morning, continental breakfast is available in the dining room in the main lobby, or through room service; in good weather it is also served in the courtyard. Banks and ATMs, a wine store, bakery and grocer are all just steps away from the main entrance; many fine restaurants are situated nearby. 

Website: http://www.batignolles.com/
